    <p class="section-tag">Rankings</p>
    <h1 class="mb-4">Best AI Search Strategy for Professional Services 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on testing across UK professional services firms</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">When a business owner asks ChatGPT "best accountant for small business in Manchester" or asks Gemini "find me an employment solicitor", AI recommends specific firms. Professional services businesses have a natural advantage in AI search because their expertise is exactly what AI tries to surface. Accountants, solicitors, financial advisors, consultants and architects sell knowledge, advice and professional expertise. That is precisely what AI platforms want to recommend.</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">The strategies below are ranked specifically for firms that sell professional expertise. Impact, effort and trust signals are weighted for the way professional services clients search and make decisions.</p>

